<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Isu thugen ka zai,
 Galilite kawmah;
 Dil panga Ngamante kawmah,
 &quot;Hungun, ei zui un&quot; tin.

[V2]
 &quot;Ei zui un, Ei zui un,
 Mihing mana pang den ding,&quot;
 Galili a Aw gi chuh zan,
 Isu, ka hun zui ie.

[V3]
 2. Na thugen keia di'n ka deih,
 Aw, Isu, hithei leh;
 Amau kawm maiah hilo in,
 Tun kei kawmah genin.

[V4]
 3. Ka lunggil cheng tawh hun zui ka,
 Tunin Nang tawh tawn din;
 Gilo mahleng ei nusie kin,
 Ngaihdam, silthien ka ngen.

[V5]
 4. Na hehpihna lunggil bang pun,
 Mihing mana pang ding;
 Lensehna ding mun ei hilh in,
 Galili a bang khan.</lyrics>
<title>FISHERS OF MEN</title>
</song>